Company Overview of Speece Thorson Capital Group Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Speece Thorson Capital Group Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals, including high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, and charitable organizations. It also caters to pooled investment vehicles and state and municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client focused equity portfolios along with an investment vehicle. It invests in public equity markets across the globe. The firm invests in value stocks of small to mid-cap companies. It employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to make its investments. The firm makes in-house research to make its investments. Speece Tho...
Speece Thorson Capital Group Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals, including high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, and charitable organizations. It also caters to pooled investment vehicles and state and municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client focused equity portfolios along with an investment vehicle. It invests in public equity markets across the globe. The firm invests in value stocks of small to mid-cap companies. It employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to make its investments. The firm makes in-house research to make its investments. Speece Thorson Capital Group Inc. was founded in 1992 and is based at Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Detailed Description


